                        <ab>The sections are numbered in a late hand up to 106: the last is</ab>
                        <rubric locusNew="89r">de epilogo philosophi in oratione sua</rubric>
                        <explicit locus="89v">Sicut etiam beatus <name type="person">paulus</name> omnes epistolas suas
