                            concludamus</explicit>
                        <rubric locus="89v">Explicit summa de arte predicandi quam fecit magister <name type="author"
                                >thomas de salesbiriensi</name></rubric>
                        <ab>This copy is mentioned by <ref type="bibl" target="Tanner 1748">Tanner</ref>. He is
                            uncertain whether the author is the same as <name type="person">Thomas of Chabeham or
                                Cobham</name>, subdean of Sarum and author of a penitential <hi rend="italic"
                            >Summa</hi></ab>
